description: The image shows a presentation during a conference. A large screen displays a slide titled "Influencer Strategy" with a graphic showing a triangle labeled "Ambiguity", "Rationale", and "Precision". The room is lit with a strong blue and purple hue. In the foreground, a woman is seated on the left, holding a white cup. On the right of the screen, a man, seemingly a photographer, is taking pictures. The setting is a conference hall with draped curtains.
